* {{ill|Kin-gū|ja|金武宮|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Oki-no-gū‎|ja|沖宮|1=Oki-no-gū‎|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Shikina-gū|ja|識名宮|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Ameku-gū|ja|天久宮|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* {{ill|Sueyoshi-gū|ja|末吉宮|qq=draft|qq=draft}}}}, and a plan was proposed to develop the local utaki shrines into shrines. This idea was first proposed around 1939, and was featured in a newspaper article on August 27, 1940 (Showa 15) as "One Village, One Company" {{Sfn|加治順人|2018}} .The one village, one shrine concept was initially shelved due to lack of funds, but in 1943 the prefecture applied to the national government for grants to restore the [[eight Ryukyu shrines]]. In addition, five new shrines were designated as prefectural shrines {{Refn|{{ill|Futemma-gū|ja|普天満宮|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Sefa-utaki|lt=Saiba Shrine|ja|斎場神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ({{ill|Sefa-utaki|ja|斎場御嶽|qq=draft|qq=draft}}), {{ill|Nakijin Castle|lt=Hokuzan Shrine|ja|北山神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ({{ill|Nakijin Castle|ja|今帰仁城|qq=draft|qq=draft}}), {{ill|Miyako Shrine|ja|宮古神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, and {{ill|Yaeyama Shrine|ja|八重山神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (possibly {{ill|Ōishigaki Utaki|ja|大石垣御嶽|qq=draft|qq=draft}}){{sfn|後田多敦ほか|2020|pp=25-28}} make up the five shrines{{sfn|加治順人|2018|pp=53-55}}.|group=Note}}, and a plan was drawn up to consolidate the more than 900 Utaki shrines into 60 village shrines and 150 subordinate shrines. {{Sfn|加治順人|2018}} Among the utaki that have been converted into shrines are {{ill|Shirogane-do|8=en|10=ja|11=白銀堂|qq=draft|qq=draft}} in {{ill|Itoman|8=en|10=ja|11=糸満市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Tsukishiro-gu Shrine|8=en|10=ja|11=月代宮|qq=draft|qq=draft}} in {{ill|Sashiki|8=en|10=ja|11=南城市|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Nanjō|8=en|10=ja|11=佐敷町_(沖縄県)|qq=draft|qq=draft}},  {{ill|Sōkei-gu Shrine|8=en|10=ja|11=惣慶宮|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and {{ill|Awase Shrine|8=en|10=ja|11=泡瀬神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}} in {{ill|Ginoza village|8=en|10=ja|11=宜野座村|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Shinzato-gu Shrine|8=en|10=ja|11=新里宮|qq=draft|qq=draft}} in {{ill|Motobu, Okinawa|fr|Motobu|zh|本部町|8=en|10=ja|11=本部町|qq=draft|qq=draft}},  {{ill|Toyama Shrine|8=en|10=ja|11=十山神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}} in {{ill|Yonaguni town|8=en|10=j